#: ../GDebi/GDebiGtk.py:666
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Please check your internet connection or installation medium, and make sure "
"your APT cache is up-to-date."
msgstr "인터넷 연결 또는 설치 매체를 확인 하십시오."

#: ../GDebi/GDebiGtk.py:672
